
### 5. Refresh Token ###

# Authentication Code Grant Type, Resource Owner Password Credentials Grant 에서
# AccessToken이 만료되었을 경우 RefreshToken을 이용하여 토큰 재발행.

### 5 - 1 RefreshToken으로 토큰 재발행
POST http://localhost:8080/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic YmFjdG9yaWE6cGFzc3dvcmQh # client_id:client_password (Not User)

grant_type=refresh_token&scope=read_profile&refresh_token=########-####-####-####-############

